<section class="clawmart section" id="clawmart">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="clawmart__card glass-card">
      <div class="clawmart__content">
        <div class="clawmart__header">
          <h2 class="clawmart__title">
            Run your own <span class="text-gradient">Aleister</span>
          </h2>
          <span class="clawmart__price">$99</span>
        </div>
        <p class="clawmart__desc">
          Curious what it's like to have an AI orchestrator managing your workflows?
          Aleister is available as a persona on ClawMart — clone the full setup to your
          own OpenClaw instance and make it yours.
        </p>
        <ul class="clawmart__features">
          <li>Complete persona with SOUL.md, memory system & sub-agent playbook</li>
          <li>9 specialized sub-agent roles pre-configured</li>
          <li>Works on any OpenClaw Gateway setup</li>
        </ul>
        <a
          href="https://www.shopclawmart.com/listings/aleister-ec18b8ae"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="btn btn-primary clawmart__cta"
        >
          View on ClawMart →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .clawmart {
    padding: 2rem 0 4rem;
  }

  .clawmart__card {
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: var(--bg-glass);
  }

  .clawmart__content {
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .clawmart__header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .clawmart__title {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .clawmart__price {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    border-radius: 20px;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--text-accent) 12%, transparent);
    color: var(--text-accent);
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--text-accent) 25%, transparent);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .clawmart__desc {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .clawmart__features {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .clawmart__features li {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .clawmart__features li::before {
    content: "✓";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--text-accent);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .clawmart__cta {
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .clawmart__card {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .clawmart__header {
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .clawmart__content {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .clawmart__features {
      align-items: center;
    }

    .clawmart__features li {
      padding-left: 1.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
